name: Rajd Przez Polske
overview: Rajd przez Polske is an arcade racing game allowing to drive three old Polish cars: Polonez Caro, Fiat 126p and Fiat Cinquecento. The player drive through multiple roads between the larger cities of Poland. The goal requires reaching the destination point before the time runs out. Hitting the roadside or another car causing the loss of speed. All three cars differ in maximum speed. The game allows to choose one of six available sound tracks.
